<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:27:42 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>柯达数码相机</title><link>https://some.pics/69da221bd7267</link><description>&lt;p&gt;柯达数码相机&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="KODAK Digital Still Camera" height="3456" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dogsofparis/69da221bd7267.jpg" width="4608"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dogsofparis.some.pics"&gt;@dogsofparis&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:27:42 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>塔科阿河火车风光</title><link>https://some.pics/69da1e328fd6c</link><description>&lt;p&gt;从火车上看到的塔科阿河景色。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A serene riverside scene with clear water reflecting a bright blue sky and lush green trees lining the banks, creating a peaceful, natural setting." height="2893" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da1e328fd6c.jpg" width="3857"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:11:01 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>麦凯斯维尔甜点店</title><link>https://some.pics/69da1e0431042</link><description>&lt;p&gt;甜美的艾玛琳芝士蛋糕店，是我们在乔治亚州麦凯斯维尔这座古雅小镇探访的特色店铺之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Cozy cheesecake shop with wood decor; three customers, one at a fridge, two seated. Counter with menu displays in the background. Warm and inviting atmosphere." height="2810" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da1e0431042.jpg" width="3747"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:10:17 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>麦凯斯维尔甜点店</title><link>https://some.pics/69da1dd6bdbe5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;甜美的艾玛琳芝士蛋糕店，是我们在乔治亚州麦凯斯维尔这座古雅小镇探访的特色店铺之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='Displays of mini cheesecakes in clear plastic containers, labeled "Sweet Emmaline." Varied toppings; a sign reads "6 Pack $15.49." Tempting and colorful.' height="2655" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da1dd6bdbe5.jpg" width="3540"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:09:29 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>蓝岭铁路之旅</title><link>https://some.pics/69da1dacbd018</link><description>&lt;p&gt;昨天我们乘坐了蓝岭铁路的列车。它从佐治亚州蓝岭市中心的历史车站出发，沿着托科阿河进行四小时、26英里的往返旅程，途经佐治亚州的麦凯斯维尔和田纳西州的科珀希尔，然后返回车站。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A round, yellow sign with "Blue Ridge Railway" in bold text and a small blue train graphic above. It includes "Blue Ridge, Georgia" at the top.' height="2578" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/69da1dacbd018.jpg" width="3437"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 Apr 2026 10:08:47 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>